                <div class="div-hero-split-card">
                    <h2 class="div-split-title">Mining, Material Handling, Processing &amp; Balance of Plant</h2>
                    <p class="div-split-desc">Established in 1976, the Mining, Material Handling and Processing Business Vertical of TKIL Industries has been at the forefront of transforming the mining, material handling, and comminution (crushing and grinding) sectors in India. Over the years, we have built a strong reputation for delivering innovative and sustainable solutions to industries such as open cast mining, power, ports, steel, fertilizers, and minerals.</p>
                    <p class="div-split-desc">Leveraging world-class technology, our extensive portfolio includes advanced conveyor systems, comprehensive stockyard equipment — stackers, reclaimers, and stacker-cum-reclaimers — a broad range of crushers, screens, and feeders including our MACS vertical, and wet ball mill systems for FGD applications. We have also established a strong presence in the Balance of Plant (BoP) segment of the thermal power industry, extending our global footprint through strategic collaborations with leading international technology partners.</p>
                    <p class="div-split-desc">With nearly five decades of experience, we continue to push the boundaries of innovation and engineering excellence — committed to creating long-term value through strategic partnerships and sustainable practices that drive India's industrial growth.</p>
