                    <h2 class="div-split-title">Cement Plants &amp; Equipment</h2>
                    <p class="div-split-desc">The Cement business vertical of TKIL Industries carries a rich legacy of delivering engineering solutions, high-performance equipment, and systems for cement plants — spanning raw grinding, pyro processing, cement grinding, and automation, all the way to complete plant machinery through thyssenkrupp Polysius technology. This association with a leading global technology provider ensures superior productivity, optimum plant availability, and reduced energy consumption for our customers.</p>
                    <p class="div-split-desc">With a proven global project footprint across Bahrain, Bangladesh, Benin, Burkina Faso, Côte d'Ivoire, Ghana, Indonesia, Kenya, Malawi, Mozambique, Nepal, Sri Lanka, Sudan, Togo, UAE, and Uganda, TKIL Industries is a trusted partner to leading cement manufacturers worldwide — focused on energy-efficient and sustainable solutions.</p>
                    <p class="div-split-desc">Our Cement Services vertical delivers comprehensive aftermarket support across the full equipment lifecycle — covering spares, upgrades, and turnkey solutions for Kilns, Coolers, VRMs, Ball Mills, and POLYCOMs, alongside in-house expertise in Hot Kiln Alignment, In-Situ Grinding, Condition Monitoring, process audits, and plant optimization aimed at reducing emissions and improving long-term performance.</p>
