            mining: {
                items: [
                    {
                        id: "mining-equip",
                        title: "Equipment and Systems for Material Handling Plant",
                        children: [
                            { id: "mining-stackers", title: "Stackers", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/stacker-1.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/stacker.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>In any large scale stockyard operation, one of the major functions is stacking the material. TKIL Industries manufactures Rail Mounted Stackers in a variety of configurations. These rugged, operator friendly stackers are designed after carefully taking into consideration functional requirements like throughput, mobility and automation (semi or fully automatic) as well as operational requirements like luffing and slewing.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-bucket-wheel", title: "Bucket Wheel Reclaimers", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/Bucket-Wheel-Reclaimers.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/Bucket-Wheel-Reclaimers-1.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>TKIL Industries manufactures the whole range of stacking and reclaiming machines for stockyards. Available with either fully or semi-automatic control systems, these machines guarantee uniform reclaiming of stockpile and the highest degree of economy and efficiency.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-combined-stacker", title: "Combined Stacker Reclaimers", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/stacker-cum-reclaimer3.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/stacker-cum-reclaimer4.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>Combined Stacker-Reclaimers are single unit machines which can operate in both stacking and reclaiming modes separately. They also permit a high degree of automation in both modes of operation. Can be used for blending / mixing different types of coal for power plant applications.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-stockyard", title: "Other Stockyard Equipment", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/Other-Stockyard-Equipment.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/Other-Stockyard-Equipment-1.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>TKIL Industries designs, manufactures and supplies stockyard machines like Bridge-Type Scraper Reclaimers, Portal and Semi-Portal Scraper Reclaimers, Circular Stacker Reclaimers and Side Scraper Reclaimers.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-feeders", title: "Feeders", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/feeders.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/Feeders-1.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>TKIL Industries offers Apron Feeders in different sizes and capacities for a wide range of applications.</p><h4>Product Range</h4><ul><li>Apron Feeders</li><li>Chain Feeders</li><li>Reciprocating Feeders</li><li>Vibrating Feeders</li></ul>` },
                            { id: "mining-paddle-feeders", title: "Paddle Feeders", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/paddle-feeders.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/paddle-feeder-1.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>TKIL Industries Paddle Feeders ensure high reliability, compactness in design, low power consumption, operational simplicity and ease in capacity variation.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-screens", title: "Screens", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/Screen-feeders-1.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/Roller-Screen.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>A range of high efficiency Screens for screening before or after crushing.</p><h4>Product Range</h4><ul><li>Vibrating Screens (Circular and Linear)</li><li>Roller Screens</li><li>Grizzly Screens</li><li>Wobbler Feeders</li></ul>` },
                            { id: "mining-crushers", title: "Crushers", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/Crushers.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>TKIL Industries offers a wide range of Crushers designed to take on any crushing job.</p><h4>Product Range</h4><ul><li>Double Roll Crushers</li><li>Ring Hammer Mill / Ring Granulator</li><li>Rotary Breakers</li><li>Jaw Crushers</li><li>Hammer Mills</li><li>Cone Crushers</li></ul>` },
                            { id: "mining-wagon-tipplers", title: "Wagon Tipplers", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/wagon-tippler.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/wagon-tippler1.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>TKIL Industries manufactures a wide range of Tipplers, including Side Discharge Tipplers and Rotary Tipplers for railway wagons as per revised RDSO G33 (Rev-1) guidelines.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-curved-conveyors", title: "Long-Distance Curved Conveyors", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/overland-conveyor-1.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/overland-conveyor.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. has a large presence in the field of Cross Country Conveyors and Pipe Conveyors, manufacturing critical components like idlers and pulleys in its own facilities.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-idler-rollers", title: "Idler Rollers and Pulleys", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/Idler-Rollers.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/Pulleys.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>TKIL Industries precision idler rollers are the product of choice for high-speed and pipe conveyors. Every single idler roller undergoes a freewheel test before delivery.</p><h4>Pulleys</h4><p>TKIL Industries conveyor pulleys feature keyless connection between hub and end disc, post-weld heat treatment, balance to ISO 1940 grade G40, and stress analysis using FEM software.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-pipe-conveyors", title: "Pipe Conveyors", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/pipe-conveyor.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/pipe-conveyor-2.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>TKIL Industries Pipe Conveyors are manufactured from high-grade materials and proven components to give maximum reliability.</p><h4>Advantages</h4><ul><li>Ability to negotiate 3-D curves, resulting in minimum requirement of transfer points.</li><li>Material being transported is protected from wind, rain and other environmental hazards.</li><li>Dust and air-borne emission is avoided.</li></ul>` }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        id: "mining-special",
                        title: "Specialty Equipment",
                        content: `
                            <div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;">
                                <img src="/images/products/mhe/FGD-WBM.jpg" alt="FGD-WBM" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" />
                                <img src="/images/products/mhe/WBM-3D-GA.jpg" alt="WBM-3D-GA" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" />
                            </div>
                            <p>Apart from crushing &amp; screening we are providing machinery &amp; equipment for grinding system for wet limestone used in Flue Gas Desulphurization.</p>
                            <p><strong>GRINDING SYSTEM</strong></p>
                            <p>The system is designed to grind the limestone to fineness of up to 325 mesh for FGD application. The system comprises of feeders, grinding mill, hydro-cyclones &amp; slurry pumps for product separation and slurry handling unit.</p>
                        `
                    },
                    {
                        id: "mining-macs",
                        title: "MACS",
                        children: [
                            { id: "mining-macs-jaw", title: "Jaw Crushers", content: `<p><b>Proven quality – great flexibility – easy operation</b></p><p>TKIL Industries Jaw Crushers are used for Primary Crushing. The material is crushed by compressive &amp; shear forces. Flywheels with high moment of Inertia are generating high crushing energy &amp; compensate crusher peak loads.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-macs-cone", title: "Cone Crushers", content: `<p><b>Proven quality – great flexibility – easy operation</b></p><p>In the Cone Crusher the material is crushed by compressive forces between the Crusher shell &amp; mantle. Cone Crusher are used for Secondary &amp; Tertiary Crushing.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-macs-vsi", title: "VSI (Vertical Shaft Impactor)", content: `<p><b>Proven quality – great flexibility – easy operation</b></p><p>Vertical Shaft Impactors are tertiary crushers for the production of high-grade chippings or crushed sand from hard rock such as basalt, granite, diorite, andesite and gravel.</p>` },
                            { id: "mining-macs-screen", title: "Vibrating Screen", content: `<p><b>Proven quality – great flexibility – easy operation</b></p><p>Circular Motion Vibrating Screens are used for screening of rock, ore, coal and similar bulk materials as well as in recycling and waste disposal.</p>` },
                            {
                                id: "mining-macs-aggregate",
                                title: "Aggregate Crushing and Screening Plants",
                                children: [
                                    { id: "mining-macs-aggregate-stationary", title: "Stationary / Skid Mounted Crushing & Screening Plant", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/Aggregate-crushing-and-screening-plant.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/Aggregate-crushing-and-screening-plant-1.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>We offer a comprehensive range of equipment and services for Stationary / skid mounted two-stage, three-stage and four-stage configurations with processing capacities ranging from 150 TPH to 300 TPH.</p>` },
                                    { id: "mining-macs-aggregate-semi", title: "Semi Mobile Crushing & Screening Plant", content: `<div class="prd-inline-media" style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;"><img src="/images/products/mhe/MULTIROAD-FM90-CK804.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /><img src="/images/products/mhe/MULTIROAD-G90-CK803.jpg" loading="lazy" style="width:220px;height:160px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;" /></div><p>We offer a comprehensive range of equipment and services for Semi mobile two-stage and three-stage configurations with processing capacities ranging from 150 TPH to 250 TPH.</p>` }
                                ]
